@node Introduction "Psycho: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Psycho is a plugin for the famous image-manipulation-program
   ArtEffect2/3+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect's
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   Psycho is a fun-filter. It has a very astonishing effect.
   Strongly depending on the picture (best on real photos with strong edges,
   e.g. buildings) it traces the edges with black lines and is generating very
   colorful fillings or shine around the edges.

@endnode

